<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued December 28 at 8:06AM MST until December 29 at 8:00AM MST by NWS GrandJunction</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM MST WEDNESDAY...
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 2 to 6 inches.
* WHERE...Central Colorado River Basin.
* WHEN...Until 8 AM MST Tuesday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning or evening commute. A
detailed map of the snowfall can be found at:
www.weather.gov/gjt/winter.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.
The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.</instruction>
